(78, 2, '2011-07-29 15:13:46', '2011-07-29 22:13:46', '<em class="highlight">What is Physical Therapy?</em> Physical therapy is about the special obligation that the physical therapist has to empower, educate and enable those with impairments, activity limitations, participation restrictions and disabilities to facilitate great independence, health, wellness and enhanced quality of life.\r\n<cite>California Physical Therapy Board Code of Ethics</cite>\r\n\r\n<em class="highlight">Why Choose Valerie Nelson Physical Therapy?</em> Our mission is to provide top-quality, customized, physical therapy services in a caring and compassionate environment. <a href="/services">More in-depth information on the services we offer &raquo;</a>', 'Welcome to Valerie Nelson Physical Therapy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-14', '', '', '2011-07-29 15:13:46', '2011-07-29 22:13:46', '', 33, 'http://orovillephysicaltherapy.com/2011/07/33-revision-14/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(121, 1, '2011-08-29 21:37:25', '2011-08-30 04:37:25', '<span class="highlight">We offer a wide spectrum of rehabilitative services:</span> General Musculoskeletal Rehabilitation: Rehabilitation for impairments ranging from neck and low back pain, ankle approaches to treatment\r\n\r\n<span class="highlight">Sports Medicine:</span> Rehabilitating injuries, from competitive sports or the “weekend athlete.”\r\n\r\n<span class="highlight">Pre-or Post-Surgical:</span> Rehabilitation before or after a surgery, which may include re-education, endurance and balance.\r\n\r\n<span class="highlight">Pelvic Floor Dysfunction:</span> Rehabilitating the weak pelvic floor muscles that may cause urinary or bowel urgency, leakage or bedwetting. These issues may be due to postpartum, pre- or post-menopause symptoms, hip, colon or prostate surgeries. Ask about our "Roll For Control" program.\r\n\r\n<a href="/assets/IMG_2587_00.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-69" title="IMG_2587_00" src="/assets/IMG_2587_00.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="266" /></a>', 'What we offer our clients', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision-22', '', '', '2011-08-29 21:37:25', '2011-08-30 04:37:25', '', 9, 'http://orovillephysicaltherapy.com/2011/08/9-revision-22/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
