(10, 1, '2011-07-26 14:45:24', '2011-07-26 21:45:24', '<h3>We offer a wide spectrum of rehabilitative services:</h3>\n<p>General Musculoskeletal Rehabilitation: Rehabilitation for impairments ranging from neck and low back pain, ankle approaches to treatment</p>\n\n<h3>Sports Medicine</h3>\n<p>Rehabilitating injuries, from competitive sports to the “weekend athlete.”</p>\n\n<h3>Pre-or Post-Surgical</h3>\n<p>Rehabilitation before or after a surgery, which may include re-education, endurance and balance.</p>\n\n<h3>Pelvic Floor Dysfunction</h3>\n<p>Rehabilitating the weak pelvic floor muscles that cause urinary or bowel urgency, leakage or bedwetting. These issues may be due to postpartum, pre- or post-menopause symptoms, hip, colon or prostate surgeries. We utilize the “roll for control” program, which focuses on specific exercises and education regarding foods/relaxation/biofeedback techniques.</p>', 'What We Offer', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision', '', '', '2011-07-26 14:45:24', '2011-07-26 21:45:24', '', 9, 'http://orovillephysicaltherapy.com/2011/9-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2011-07-26 14:48:00', '2011-07-26 21:48:00', 'Our purpose is to identify the cause of your symptoms and determine the best plan in treating them. Your first visit will include an assessment and then, you and your therapist will develop the most effective treatment plan.\r\n\r\nYou can receive treatment without a physical therapy prescription/referral. However, for insurance to cover treatment, a practitioner referral will be needed.\r\n\r\nWe accept most types of public and private insurance. As a courtesy, we confirm coverage prior to your first visit, so there are no surprises to you about the cost of your treatment. We also offer a variety of payment plans to our patients.\r\n\r\nIn California you have a choice. If you would like to be treated by our clinic, just ask your doctor! We have good relationships with local physicians.', 'How to become a patient', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'become-a-patient', '', '', '2011-09-20 13:14:37', '2011-09-20 20:14:37', '', 0, 'http://orovillephysicaltherapy.com/?page_id=11', 3, 'page', '', 0),
