(45, 1, '2011-07-26 14:57:36', '2011-07-26 21:57:36', '<h3>We offer a wide spectrum of rehabilitative services:</h3>\r\n<p>General Musculoskeletal Rehabilitation: Rehabilitation for impairments ranging from neck and low back pain, ankle approaches to treatment</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Sports Medicine</h3>\r\n<p>Rehabilitating injuries, from competitive sports to the “weekend athlete.”</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Pre-or Post-Surgical</h3>\r\n<p>Rehabilitation before or after a surgery, which may include re-education, endurance and balance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Pelvic Floor Dysfunction</h3>\r\n<p>Rehabilitating the weak pelvic floor muscles that cause urinary or bowel urgency, leakage or bedwetting. These issues may be due to postpartum, pre- or post-menopause symptoms, hip, colon or prostate surgeries. We utilize the “roll for control” program, which focuses on specific exercises and education regarding foods/relaxation/biofeedback techniques.</p>', 'What We Offer', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision-3', '', '', '2011-07-26 14:57:36', '2011-07-26 21:57:36', '', 9, 'http://orovillephysicaltherapy.com/2011/9-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
