(120, 1, '2011-08-29 21:10:47', '2011-08-30 04:10:47', '<em class="highlight">What is Physical Therapy?</em> Physical therapy is about the special obligation that the physical therapist has to empower, educate and enable those with impairments, activity limitations, participation restrictions and disabilities to facilitate great independence, health, wellness and enhanced quality of life. <cite>California Physical Therapy Board Code of Ethics</cite>\r\n\r\n<a href="/assets/IMG_3332_02.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-77" title="IMG_3332_02" src="/assets/IMG_3332_02.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="266" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em class="highlight">Why Choose Valerie Nelson Physical Therapy?</em> Our mission is to provide top-quality, customized, physical therapy services in a caring and compassionate environment. <a href="/services">More in-depth information on the services we offer »</a>', 'Welcome to Valerie Nelson Physical Therapy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-revision-22', '', '', '2011-08-29 21:10:47', '2011-08-30 04:10:47', '', 33, 'http://orovillephysicaltherapy.com/2011/08/33-revision-22/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(123, 1, '2011-09-20 13:13:55', '2011-09-20 20:13:55', 'Our purpose is to identify the cause of your symptoms and determine the best plan in treating them. Your first visit will include an assessment and then, you and your therapist will develop the most effective treatment plan.\r\n\r\nYou can receive treatment without a physical therapy prescription/referral. However, for insurance to cover treatment, a practitioner referral will be needed.\r\n\r\nWe accept most types of public and private insurance. As a courtesy, we confirm coverage prior to your first visit, so there are no surprises to you about the cost of your treatment. We also offer a variety of payment plans to our patients.\r\n\r\nIn California you have a choice. If you would like to be treated by our clinic, just ask your doctor! We have good relationships with local physicians.', 'How to become a patient', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-12', '', '', '2011-09-20 13:13:55', '2011-09-20 20:13:55', '', 11, 'http://orovillephysicaltherapy.com/2011/09/11-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
